@page "/installation"
<PageTitle>Installation - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1>Installation</h1>

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2>NuGet Package</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Install the Saascade Blazor Components library via NuGet or the .NET CLI.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>.NET CLI</h3>
        <pre><code>dotnet add package Saascade.Blazor.Components</code></pre>

        <h3>Package Manager</h3>
        <pre><code>Install-Package Saascade.Blazor.Components</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Register Services</h2>

        <p>
            Add the design system to your <code>Program.cs</code>:
        </p>

        <pre><code>builder.Services.AddSingleton&lt;IDesignSystem&gt;(DesignSystems.Tailwind.DaisyUI);</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Add Imports</h2>

        <p>
            Add the following to your <code>_Imports.razor</code>:
        </p>

        <pre><code>@@using Saascade.Blazor.Components</code></pre>

    </section>

</main>
